Description: client library for the Qdrant vector search engine
 Qdrant (read: quadrant) is a vector similarity search engine. It
 provides a production-ready service with a convenient API to store,
 search, and manage points (i.e. vectors) with an additional payload.
 .
 This package provides the official Python client library for Qdrant,
 including both synchronous and asynchronous clients, gRPC and REST
 transport support, and local (in-memory or on-disk) execution mode.
